                                PNG, MP4, MOV, AVI.</small>
                            <div id="currentFileDisplay" class="mt-2"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3" id="linkUrlSection" style="display: none;">
                            <label for="link_url" class="form-label">URL Link</label>
